305
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,880
Fine.

306
00:24:24,640 --> 00:24:26,660
You little brat.

307
00:24:29,283 --> 00:24:31,289
   

308
00:24:32,169 --> 00:24:34,229
   

309
