Why don't we calculate your debt?

323
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:23,200
Or you can take another look

324
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:25,180
at who the boss here is?

325
00:25:27,300 --> 00:25:31,980
I know, I know you are the boss.

326
00:25:31,980 --> 00:25:34,240
How about your dignity?

327
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:42,940
You brat, add her.

328
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:05,060
