329
00:26:05,660 --> 00:26:06,940
 Did you watch the match yesterday? 

330
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:07,900
 Yes, I did. 

331
00:26:07,900 --> 00:26:10,081
 - It was amazing. 
 - Very good. 

332
00:26:10,081 --> 00:26:13,140
