00:28:00,120 --> 00:28:01,760
You got here really fast.

368
00:28:01,760 --> 00:28:03,760
Not as fast as you who can fly.

369
00:28:03,760 --> 00:28:05,100
Who will attack first?

370
00:28:05,100 --> 00:28:06,580
You, you do it first.

371
00:28:06,580 --> 00:28:09,800
You first, and we Tyrannical Ambition will follow.

372
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:12,260
We can attack first, but don't try to steal if you dare.

373
00:28:12,260 --> 00:28:15,240
Exactly. I don't want to die for Tyrannical Ambition.

374
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,261
You're one to talk.

375
00:28:16,261 --> 00:28:18,920
As a man dumped by Lord Grim, it's shameful for you to even be here.

376
00:28:18,920 --> 00:28:21,321
Shame on you. Did you plant a spy in my guild again?

377
00:28:21,321 --> 00:28:25,080
Old Blue, you were dumped? So miserable.

378
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:27,940
I really want to see how green* your face is right now. 
  (*Embarrassment) 

379
00:28:27,940 --> 00:28:29,560
Not greener than your Herb Garden's faces.

380
00:28:29,560 --> 00:28:31,520
All right, cut the crap.

381
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:34,340
Soon, the more guilds come, the less chance we have.

382
00:28:35,280 --> 00:28:38,280
Why don't we do this together?

383
00:28:38,280 --> 00:28:39,420
How about it?

384
00:28:39,420 --> 00:28:41,220
- Fine. 
 - Fine.

385
