00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:27,520
Facing Blood Gunner's shooting from all directions, and he's not hurt at all.

393
00:29:27,520 --> 00:29:29,480
Damn, he's impressive.

394
00:29:29,480 --> 00:29:31,700
So cool.

395
00:29:32,880 --> 00:29:35,140
Steamed Bun Invasion? Where did such an expert come from? 
    

396
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:41,460
Nice knee attack.

397
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:43,880
He counterattacks while being attacked.

398
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:45,200
His game sense is not bad.

399
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:47,600
Here comes another expert.

