403
00:30:02,020 --> 00:30:05,620
Why is he aiming at its head?

404
00:30:16,840 --> 00:30:19,140
His game sense is equal to nothing.

405
00:30:19,140 --> 00:30:20,081
That's impressive.

406
00:30:20,081 --> 00:30:23,140
I have never seen such a cool method of suicide before.

407
00:30:23,140 --> 00:30:25,240
I thought it was a big meat bun,

408
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:27,620
