471
00:34:28,900 --> 00:34:30,860
Okay.

472
00:34:30,860 --> 00:34:32,460
Uppercut.

473
00:34:41,580 --> 00:34:44,981
Bun, at the one o'clock direction, hide behind the large stone. Stay safe.

